@ Gordon Products Inc. - Custom Capability in Off-the-Shelf Sensors

















































Welcome!

To Gordon Products...the Home of Capacitive and Inductive Sensing Solutions.
        Browse around, gather information and while you do, keep in mind that our standard products are 
        often quite easily modified to suit custom applications.
Please, contact us if you would like to speak with an engineer about
        your application.








Gordon Products, Incorporated has a 25-year history of 
development and innovation in the areas of capacitive and inductive sensing.
Throughout that time we have been committed to providing our customers with the 
highest quality products and services available.
Our goal is to provide you with sensors that are easily adapted to specialized 
applications - Off-the-Shelf, at affordable prices. The way we accomplish 
this is through the use of sensors with expandable sensing elements or remote sensing capabilities. 

Occasionally, the details of an application (or the requirements of an OEM customer)
demand that we modify an existing product or design a new, application-specific sensor.
Our ability to do this is facilitated by the location of all engineering and manufacturing
in the United States of America, and we have provided these services to 
hundreds of OEM customers.
Just call or e-mail 
to get application and engineering assistance, pricing and delivery. We maintain an 
"in stock" position on all of our standard products, and we make them available for 
evaluation on a 30-Day Free Trial basis. In addition, all Gordon 
Products sensors and switches come with a Lifetime Warranty.




 


 








